title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“After much adieu, the TC by Masarati Sports Coupe has finally arrived.” [a caption in Black Enterprise, November 1988, p. 108. Submitted by John Durant Cooke, New York City.]
